title: Video Hits 86-96 DVD
description:
Video Hits is celebrating their 20th year on television this year and have teamed up with EMI in an exciting new partnership to release 2 CDs and 2 DVDs chronicling the best and most memorable songs and videos from the last twenty years.

Volume 1 covers the first ten years and features 40 classic music videos from between 1986 and 1996 from artists as diverse as Rick Astley, INXS, George Michael, Bananarama, Kylie Minogue, Faith No More, Deee-Lite, Sinead O&#039;Connor, Tina Arena, Take That, Everything But The Girl and many more.
